         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">5/4/79 ¶ Herewith, dear Dr Beccari, I send you the fruits of a new Areca from Trinity Bay. ¶  The species is allied to A. triandra &amp; A. oxycarpa. I have sent the description to Dr von Regels Garten-Fl...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">79.04.05</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Odoardo Beccari</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">University of Florence, Science Library: Botany, Archives, Beccari 12/32.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">5/4/79</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Herewith, dear Dr Beccari, I send you the fruits of a new Areca from Trinity Bay.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>North Qld.</p>
               </note> The species is allied to A. triandra &amp; A. oxycarpa. I have sent the description to Dr von Regels Garten-Flora.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Areca alicae</seg>, B79.07.06.</p>
               </note> Let me thank you for the <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">splendid</hi>
               </seg> 3th fascicle of the Malesia!<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Beccari (1877-90); fascicle 3 was published in September 1878 (TL2).</p>
               </note> In what <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">treasures</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">you</hi>
               </seg> are revelling!! I quite envie you about your <name key="Rhododendron">Rhododendron</name>s &amp;c.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I hope you will let me have soon the <name key="Leguminosae">Leguminosae</name>, as I like to elaborate them first. Dr Scheffer has sent me a large lot of <name key="Rubiaceae">Rubiaceae</name>, which seem mostly known,<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to O. Beccari, 16 February 1879.</p>
               </note> and which I must retain until I have <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">your</hi>
               </seg>
               <name key="Rubiaceae">Rubiaceae</name>.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Pray remember me to Dr Giglioli and let me remain your regardful</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
